title: Active@ Boot Disk Suite 10.1.0 Modified Edition Dec. 2015 (ISO)
description:
Active@ Boot Disk Suite 10.1.0 Modified Edition Dec. 2015 (ISO)

This modified version of Active@ Boot Disk Suite 10.1.0 includes tons of additional tools.

Active@ Boot Disk original tools

Active@ Disk Image - for backing up your disks
Active@ Password Changer - for resetting your local password
Active@ KillDisk - for hard drive erasing
Active@ File Recovery - for data recovery
Active@ Partition Recovery - for advanced partition recovering
Active@ Hard Disk Monitor - for HDD monitoring
Active@ Partition Manager - for partition creation & editing
Active@ Data CD/DVD Burner - for burning data disks
Network Utilities - for network configuration & access
System Utilities - all useful tools for system
Internet Utilities - for browsing web, etc.
Console tools - DiskPart, PowerShell...
